t: Amazon Dates and UTC Explained – Marketplace Reporting
s: Amazon records dates in Coordinated Universal Time or UTC. UTC is the primary standard used to regulate clocks and time by the world and is not adjusted for daylight saving time. Greenwich Mean Time (GMT) is the predecessor to UTC and effectively means the same as UTC.
